  id: wfo_sftdc_03
  displayName: Hospital Target
  description: 'The army claims the enemy is positioned inside a hospital building
    and wants to strike it.

    If carried out, the offensive could accelerate military
    progress.

    However, the risk of civilian casualties and international backlash
    is extremely high.

    They request your media support to justify and shape
    public perception of the operation.'
  devNote: "feed skilli olu\u015Fturulunca 2. choice i\xE7in \xF6n ko\u015Ful olarak
    eklenecek"
  eventNote: "ordu ilerlemesi i\xE7in \xF6nemli oldu\u011Funu d\xFC\u015F\xFCnerek
    birka\xE7 tane hastane vurmay\u0131 ister\nsenden de istedi\u011Fi bu operasyonun
    alg\u0131 aya\u011F\u0131n\u0131 \xFCstlenmen\nkabul edip medyada alg\u0131 pompalayarak
    operasyonu me\u015Frula\u015Ft\u0131rmaya \xE7al\u0131\u015Fabilirsin, itibar\u0131n
    d\xFC\u015Fer ancak war supportun ciddi oranda artar\nreddedebilirsin, itibar\u0131n
    artar, siyasi n\xFCfuzun biraz azal\u0131r, war supportun d\xFC\u015Fer. ayr\u0131ca
    protest tetiklenme ihtimalini de y\xFCzde 20 kadar artt\u0131r\u0131r"
  minWarTime: 30
  maxWarTime: -1
  decisionTime: 20
